room_title: Escape room "Save the Asylum" by EscapeTech in Salem
room_description:
Imagine that you and your group work for the famous, Salem Asylum. Lately, one of your patients has been acting strange, one day, while the patient leaves his room, you decide to take a look.
Within the room, you discover his plot to commit a massive crime on the people of the Asylum. You have 60 minutes to unlock the door and stop him, or you and the Asylum are history...
